<br>• Chances of rejections of the transplants
<br>• 2 or 3 (or more) hair transplants normally needed to achieve</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:2"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-174_"></div></div></div><div class="sc-dPiLbb jGEmDy pf-175_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:2"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-176_"></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:8"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXeWAj cnchaw pf-177_"><a data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-llYSUQ kDdaXh pf-178_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-iWVNaa eCsXSR pf-180_">About Maintenance</span></a><div class="sc-fKVqWL clixrC pf-181_ pf-icon-right" data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-bBHxTw QejWU pf-182_"><button type="button" class="sc-dlVxhl hZTTUa pf-183_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="141eb781-a48d-4c7c-ba16-16e8440c9f93" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>
